  "rationale": "<p>Choice C is correct. The <em>x</em>-intercept occurs where <em>y</em> = 0. Setting 9<em>x</em> \u2212 63 = 0 gives 9<em>x</em> = 63, so <em>x</em> = 7. The <em>x</em>-intercept is (7, 0).</p><p>Choices A, B, and D are incorrect; they correspond to sign errors or misidentifying coefficients.</p>",
